plot: Moe is faced with a difficult choice when Evergreen Terrace develops a traffic problem.

When Evergreen Terrace is overrun by traffic from an app used by the citizens. Homer and his family try to resolve the issue, they enlist Professor Frink to take care of the situation and he makes the street disappear from the database. Meanwhile, Moe rekindles his relationship with his ex-girlfriend, Maya. Moe becomes afraid that Maya will reject him again, he hides in Bart's treehouse. Homer encourages Moe to propose to Maya. Moe comes back to his bar and he apologizes to Maya for avoiding her. Moe proposes to Maya and she accepts.—dawsonpersi
